    - TextDirect: The Gem pulses fitfully, giving a sensation of pulling upward. 
    - TextDirect: You hear a faint voice in the back of your mind. It sounds female, and really tired.
    - TextDirect: "Hello? I can feel your presence, faintly. I can't move. The Undead brought me up to this tower. They carried me through some large castle, and into a Great Hall. The last thing I remember passing before they opened the portal to this tower was a throne of some kind. Please help me. You're my only hope."
